---

<section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background with gradient overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy-900">
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-navy-900 via-navy-800 to-navy-900 opacity-80"
        >
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative blobs -->
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center"
    >
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight"
        >
            Prêt à réussir votre concours ?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Rejoignez dès maintenant la communauté des futurs Sapeurs-Pompiers
            Professionnels et donnez-vous les moyens de vos ambitions.
        </p>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4"
        >
            <a
                href="https://app.casqueenmains.fr"
                class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-accent/25 hover:shadow-accent/40 hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center"
            >
                Télécharger l'application
                <svg
                    class="ml-2 w-5 h-5"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    ><path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg
                >
            </a>
            <a
                href="/tarifs"
                class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-full glass text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-200 text-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            >
                Voir les tarifs
            </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
            7 jours d'essai • Sans engagement • Annulation à tout moment
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
